    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、{user}さん！\nこっち！　こっちですよ！",
      "startTime": 2.4666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2266.6666666,
          "startTime": 4.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、遅くなってすまない\n衣装合わせのアポイントまで、ほとんど時間がないな",
      "startTime": 9.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ！　{user}さんは担当アイドルが\nすっっっごい沢山いますし、少しくらい平気です",
      "startTime": 16.8129889806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "お忙しいのは分かってますから！",
      "startTime": 21.0796556473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "愛は絶対に遅刻しないよな……何時に来たんだ？",
      "startTime": 23.6129889806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "いつも三十分前でしょうか\n私、相手をお待たせするのが心苦しくて……",
      "startTime": 31.146322314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "愛の言う通り過ぎて、今は俺が心苦しいよ……\nいっそ莉央さんみたいに怒ってくれた方が気が楽だ",
      "startTime": 40.146322314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません、{user}さんに\n嫌味を言った訳じゃありません！",
      "startTime": 46.0129889806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "私、{user}さんには\n毎日が大感謝デーですから！",
      "startTime": 51.1129889806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "むしろ、私なんかの担当までしていただいて\nありがたいというか、ごめんなさいというか……",
      "startTime": 57.5796556473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "何を言ってるんだ、愛は今や\nLizNoirの立派な一員じゃないか",
      "startTime": 64.6129889806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、立派なんかじゃありませんよ\n端っこが定位置の、端っこアイドルですから！",
      "startTime": 71.0129889806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "今だって、ここに立っていても誰にも\n気付かれませんでしたし",
      "startTime": 76.8129889806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それは愛が目立たないようにしてるからだろ？\n普通にしてたら、すぐに分かる。謙遜するなよ",
      "startTime": 82.2129889806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "謙遜なんてしてませんよ～！\n私には芸能人オーラがないですから",
      "startTime": 89.046322314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（そんなことはない。愛は控えめな性格だから）\n（待ち合わせでも、隅で目立たないようにしている）",
      "startTime": 95.746322314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（時には、もっと自信を持って前に出てほしいけど）",
      "startTime": 98.946322314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、どうしたんですか？\n難しい顔をして",
      "startTime": 105.246322314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……愛、今日の衣装合わせの後、時間は取れるか？\n新しい仕事の打ち合わせをしたいんだけど",
      "startTime": 111.6129889806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "新しいお仕事！　嬉しい！\nもちろん大歓迎です！",
      "startTime": 117.7129889806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ただし、この仕事に『端っこ』はないぞ\n愛には思いっきり目立ってもらう",
      "startTime": 123.546322314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "――え？",
      "startTime": 126.5796556473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ！？　わ、私、単体でのお仕事ですか！？",
      "startTime": 129.946322314,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11483.333333299981,
          "startTime": 141.4296556473
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ。ぜひ愛に、というオファーがあったんだ\n面白い仕事だと思うぞ。詳しくはこの資料を読んでくれ",
      "startTime": 138.446322314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、えふぴーえす？　のゲームのプロモーション？\nミリタリー風の衣装を着てイベント出演……",
      "startTime": 149.4129889806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、私には無理です！",
      "startTime": 153.9796556473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "……諦めるのが早過ぎないか！？\n何が無理なんだ？",
      "startTime": 159.346322314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "私、ゲームにはぜんっぜん詳しくありません！\nFBI系のゲームって言われても全然分かりませんし",
      "startTime": 165.0796556473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "愛、連邦捜査局とは関係ない。FPSだ\nミリタリーテイストのシューティングゲームだよ",
      "startTime": 173.346322314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "ミリタリーって、兵隊さんとかそういうのですよね？\nやっぱり無理です！　私、よわよわキャラですよ！",
      "startTime": 179.8129889806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "本当に銃撃戦をする訳じゃないから……\n先方は愛のその鍛えられた体に惚れ込んだらしい",
      "startTime": 187.6129889806,
